  "prompt": "Do any of the Indian banks provide personalized gift cards where I can put a personalized image on the card?",
  "response": "Yes, several Indian banks offer personalized gift cards that allow you to upload a custom image. These cards can be used as a thoughtful gift for various occasions. Some of the banks that typically provide this service include:\n\n1. **HDFC Bank**: They offer personalized gift cards where customers can upload images and customize the card design.\n\n2. **ICICI Bank**: ICICI Bank provides personalized gift cards with options to select themes and upload personal images.\n\n3. **Axis Bank**: Axis Bank also has a feature for personalized gift cards that let you upload images.\n\n4. **State Bank of India (SBI)**: SBI offers personalized gift cards, although the customization options may vary.\n\n5. **Paytm Payments Bank**: Paytm allows you to create custom Gift Cards that can be personalized.\n\nIt\u2019s always a good idea to check directly with the bank\u2019s website or customer service for the latest offerings, as services and features can change over time.",
